WEBVTT

00:00:20.079 --> 00:00:21.280
Starting today,

00:00:21.399 --> 00:00:22.440
I'm in charge here.

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:24.120
You.

00:00:24.199 --> 00:00:25.120
Pour me a drink.

00:00:28.280 --> 00:00:30.000
All the cash A Min skimmed is right here.

00:00:31.480 --> 00:00:33.520
The punk wanted to grab the cash and bolt.

00:00:33.799 --> 00:00:34.719
Good thing I had a backup plan.

00:00:34.799 --> 00:00:36.000
I had his car tailed

00:00:36.439 --> 00:00:37.320
and we cut him off.

00:00:37.920 --> 00:00:39.240
What an idiot.

00:00:39.759 --> 00:00:41.159
Can't even run away properly.

00:00:42.359 --> 00:00:43.000
Madam,

00:00:43.320 --> 00:00:44.560
once I count it, I'll take it back to the company.

00:00:44.840 --> 00:00:45.880
The boys are waiting.

00:00:46.840 --> 00:00:48.479
This A Min mess has dragged on for days.

00:00:59.759 --> 00:01:00.560
Hold on.

00:01:03.799 --> 00:01:04.920
Take the punk away.

00:01:08.159 --> 00:01:08.840
You guys,

00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:10.200
you're with me from now on.

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:11.159
Move.

00:01:11.239 --> 00:01:11.959
Yes.

00:01:29.719 --> 00:01:30.400
Recently,

00:01:30.799 --> 00:01:32.680
an explosion struck a residential complex in the west of the city.

00:01:32.799 --> 00:01:34.519
The initial police investigation indicates

00:01:34.799 --> 00:01:37.239
it was caused by a thrown Molotov cocktail.

00:01:37.519 --> 00:01:39.920
In the case footage circulating online,

00:01:40.079 --> 00:01:42.239
the suspect has been identified as

00:01:42.239 --> 00:01:44.239
a bar owner surnamed Min.

00:01:44.439 --> 00:01:46.000
However, he remains at large.

00:01:46.239 --> 00:01:48.439
The police are conducting an all-out manhunt.

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:50.560
Today, we've invited

00:01:50.640 --> 00:01:52.359
a renowned criminology professor.

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:56.280
Why'd you turn it off?

00:01:56.519 --> 00:01:58.120
I wanted to hear what the expert had to say.

00:01:59.400 --> 00:02:00.680
What, you anxious?

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:04.439
Why would I be anxious?

00:02:06.400 --> 00:02:07.760
You're the one who should be.

00:02:08.039 --> 00:02:09.840
A case this nasty,

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:11.960
you'll have to beef up the police force again, right?

00:02:15.240 --> 00:02:16.120
Aren't you pretty close

00:02:16.199 --> 00:02:17.560
with that Feng Mao Company?

00:02:17.639 --> 00:02:19.080
Give us some leads.

00:02:21.919 --> 00:02:23.360
With things blowing up like this,

00:02:24.199 --> 00:02:26.400
this isn't just some petty squabble.

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:28.919
Could it be that Zhang Yuanshan

00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:31.120
is out for revenge against Bro Mao?

00:02:32.919 --> 00:02:33.680
No idea.

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:35.520
All I know is Zhang Yuanshan

00:02:35.560 --> 00:02:37.080
has some debts with Feng Mao.

00:02:37.479 --> 00:02:38.639
Beyond that, I don't know.

00:02:39.520 --> 00:02:40.280
The service station up ahead,

00:02:40.360 --> 00:02:41.120
pull over.

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:50.400
Bro Mao.

00:02:51.599 --> 00:02:53.080
You're that close with Chen Yongjiang?

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:54.000
"Bro Mao," he says.

00:02:58.000 --> 00:02:59.159
How could I not be?

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:00.919
He's my boss.

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:03.240
Everyone calls him Bro Mao.

00:03:03.319 --> 00:03:05.120
What else would I call him?

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:32.120
Consultant.

00:03:33.960 --> 00:03:35.240
Consultant my foot.

00:03:41.759 --> 00:03:42.479
Paopao,

00:03:42.879 --> 00:03:43.759
we're going home.

00:03:46.759 --> 00:03:47.840
Chestnut cake.

00:03:48.719 --> 00:03:49.879
Thanks for the trouble.

00:03:50.159 --> 00:03:51.400
Coming all this way.

00:03:51.479 --> 00:03:52.599
Come on, it's nothing.

00:03:52.680 --> 00:03:54.360
Just think of it as a vacation, right?

00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:56.360
Yummy, so yummy!

00:03:56.439 --> 00:03:57.199
So yummy!

00:03:57.520 --> 00:03:58.719
Aren't you gonna thank Uncle?

00:03:58.800 --> 00:04:00.120
Thank you, Uncle.

00:04:00.560 --> 00:04:02.120
After the drip, she can be discharged.

00:04:02.199 --> 00:04:04.199
Keep her away from crowded places.

00:04:11.039 --> 00:04:11.800
Brother Xiao,

00:04:12.039 --> 00:04:13.080
Madam wants to see you.

00:04:13.560 --> 00:04:15.840
Probably about that employment agreement.

00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:18.360
Okay.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:19.879
I'll go see her tomorrow.

00:04:21.759 --> 00:04:22.519
Alright.

00:04:22.839 --> 00:04:23.319
Oh, right.

00:04:23.399 --> 00:04:24.920
That last batch of money is all done.

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:28.639
A Min's channel is dead now.

00:04:29.360 --> 00:04:30.959
For now, we'll run small transactions.

00:04:31.319 --> 00:04:32.839
Keep some extra cards on you too.

00:04:33.199 --> 00:04:33.759
Got it.

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:41.399
Appreciate it.

00:05:20.279 --> 00:05:21.639
Sis, you're really not going back?

00:05:22.680 --> 00:05:23.399
No, I'm really not.

00:05:23.399 --> 00:05:24.759
I'll talk to Ya Ping later.

00:05:25.279 --> 00:05:26.879
Paopao does need a couple days to rest.

00:05:26.959 --> 00:05:27.720
We'll get together another time.

00:05:28.079 --> 00:05:28.839
All right then.

00:05:29.040 --> 00:05:30.399
But you really have to tell her, okay?

00:05:30.480 --> 00:05:32.079
Otherwise she'll think I didn't try to invite you.

00:05:32.079 --> 00:05:32.959
And she'll get on my case again.

00:05:33.319 --> 00:05:33.959
Okay.

00:05:34.279 --> 00:05:35.519
Go home and do your homework.

00:05:36.079 --> 00:05:37.920
Once it's done, I'll take you to the amusement park.

00:05:37.920 --> 00:05:38.759
How's that sound?

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:40.079
Uncle.

00:05:40.279 --> 00:05:42.959
If you don't want to take me, just say so.

00:05:43.759 --> 00:05:44.399
I really don't.

00:05:44.399 --> 00:05:45.519
What are you talking about?

00:05:45.959 --> 00:05:47.000
The kid's just joking.

00:05:47.160 --> 00:05:47.839
Salute.

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:50.759
Okay.

00:05:51.160 --> 00:05:52.000
Hurry on back now.

00:05:52.199 --> 00:05:52.920
It's cold out here.

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:54.000
Let's go, come on.

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:55.800
Brother-in-law.

00:05:59.560 --> 00:06:00.560
If you're short on money,

00:06:01.800 --> 00:06:03.040
just tell our family.

00:06:03.439 --> 00:06:05.279
We can pool it together or borrow it for you.

00:06:06.680 --> 00:06:07.639
Don't go borrowing all over the place.

00:06:08.240 --> 00:06:08.959
Okay?

00:06:12.279 --> 00:06:13.040
Don't worry.

00:06:15.480 --> 00:06:16.319
Drive safe.

00:06:16.600 --> 00:06:17.240
Okay.

00:06:28.759 --> 00:06:29.480
Brother Xiao.

00:06:32.839 --> 00:06:33.519
Brother Xiao.

00:06:35.560 --> 00:06:36.279
Brother Xiao.

00:06:41.519 --> 00:06:42.879
Madam, you needed me?

00:06:46.639 --> 00:06:47.519
Lawyer Luo.

00:06:48.120 --> 00:06:50.079
Nothing major, I just called you over

00:06:53.279 --> 00:06:54.480
to get Bro Mao to sign.

00:06:55.079 --> 00:06:56.480
He just up and walked off,

00:06:56.759 --> 00:06:58.240
left me holding the bag.

00:07:01.639 --> 00:07:02.439
Come take a quick look.

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:09.120
Stop right there.

00:08:13.839 --> 00:08:14.920
Dinner's almost ready.

00:08:21.720 --> 00:08:22.439
Ping.

00:08:23.800 --> 00:08:25.079
Hey, come here for a sec.

00:08:27.600 --> 00:08:29.199
Play later, dry your hair first.

00:08:39.279 --> 00:08:40.360
This card here

00:08:40.519 --> 00:08:41.399
has 600,000 yuan in it.

00:08:42.360 --> 00:08:43.159
For Paopao's treatment,

00:08:43.240 --> 00:08:44.720
don't worry about the money.

00:08:44.919 --> 00:08:45.720
We'll listen to the doctor.

00:08:45.799 --> 00:08:47.039
Whatever treatment she needs, we'll do it.

00:08:49.679 --> 00:08:50.840
Where did you get this money?

00:08:52.279 --> 00:08:52.960
I...

00:08:54.200 --> 00:08:55.559
took over an auto repair shop.

00:08:55.799 --> 00:08:57.000
Business has been pretty good.

00:08:57.720 --> 00:08:58.960
And I borrowed some from friends.

00:09:00.120 --> 00:09:01.840
Anyway, you just don't need to worry.

00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:03.879
Getting Paopao well is what matters most.

00:09:05.559 --> 00:09:06.279
I heard...

00:09:06.799 --> 00:09:07.799
Ya Ping told me

00:09:08.480 --> 00:09:09.919
you got fired from the law firm.

00:09:11.320 --> 00:09:12.639
What case was it over?

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:18.399
Isn't this better now?

00:09:19.159 --> 00:09:20.559
I'm free, I have time,

00:09:20.639 --> 00:09:21.799
and I can look after you two.

00:09:22.879 --> 00:09:23.639
It's good.

00:09:25.320 --> 00:09:26.080
I guess so.

00:09:27.759 --> 00:09:29.039
Anyway, what's done is done.

00:09:29.039 --> 00:09:30.759
So let's just look forward,

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:31.919
look on the bright side.

00:09:33.799 --> 00:09:35.000
Dinner in 20 minutes.

00:09:44.120 --> 00:09:46.080
Okay, it's not so cold now.

00:09:46.679 --> 00:09:48.440
Let's make tonight a bit special.

00:09:48.600 --> 00:09:49.759
Here, have some cola.

00:09:50.320 --> 00:09:51.919
Let the kid have some.

00:09:52.159 --> 00:09:52.919
Let her have some.

00:09:53.080 --> 00:09:53.919
Just this once is fine.

00:09:53.919 --> 00:09:55.039
She's had a tough time lately.

00:09:55.039 --> 00:09:55.759
Let her have some, just a little.

00:09:55.840 --> 00:09:56.960
Okay, okay, just this much.

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:57.840
Just this much.

00:09:58.440 --> 00:09:59.519
Look at your mom.

00:10:01.720 --> 00:10:03.480
Say another word and you won't even get this.

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:05.960
Don't you like this?

00:10:05.960 --> 00:10:06.759
Here, come on.

00:10:06.960 --> 00:10:07.759
Just how you like it.

00:10:11.039 --> 00:10:12.039
I forgot to pay the electric bill.

00:10:12.159 --> 00:10:13.159
I forgot too.

00:10:14.120 --> 00:10:15.679
Awesome! I knew it!

00:10:15.840 --> 00:10:17.039
Happy birthday.

00:10:17.559 --> 00:10:18.080
Wonderful.

00:10:18.080 --> 00:10:19.480
Slow down, don't bump into anything.

00:10:25.639 --> 00:10:26.799
Lately,

00:10:27.240 --> 00:10:28.200
it's been hard on you.

00:10:28.600 --> 00:10:29.720
I haven't been much help.

00:10:32.279 --> 00:10:33.879
We're each doing our part.

00:10:34.559 --> 00:10:36.200
In such a short time,

00:10:36.320 --> 00:10:37.919
you scraped together all her medical expenses.

00:10:38.200 --> 00:10:39.080
It's been hard on you too.

00:10:40.919 --> 00:10:42.720
Leaving you two out there alone,

00:10:43.399 --> 00:10:44.799
I feel really bad about it.

00:10:48.519 --> 00:10:49.960
Why are you saying that?

00:10:50.159 --> 00:10:51.000
We're family.

00:10:58.120 --> 00:10:59.240
Tonight,

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:03.240
are you staying with her?

00:11:07.600 --> 00:11:08.519
She's probably

00:11:08.879 --> 00:11:10.000
already asleep.

00:11:11.519 --> 00:11:13.000
Besides, lately,

00:11:14.159 --> 00:11:16.519
taking her to treatment, she's been pretty independent.

00:11:17.960 --> 00:11:18.960
Paopao's growing up.

00:11:33.399 --> 00:11:34.799
How come

00:11:35.039 --> 00:11:37.320
you suddenly know this position?

00:11:39.559 --> 00:11:40.440
Do you like it?

00:11:48.559 --> 00:11:50.080
Will you forgive me too?

00:12:00.480 --> 00:12:01.159
Boss.

00:12:01.639 --> 00:12:02.360
Luo Xiao is here.

00:12:22.399 --> 00:12:23.279
Lawyer Luo.

00:12:24.639 --> 00:12:25.320
Come in.

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:29.000
Come in.

00:13:24.679 --> 00:13:25.519
Is Bro Mao

00:13:27.000 --> 00:13:28.159
really dead?